pageTitle: Prime Minister’s itinerary for Wednesday, February 17, 2021 | Prime Minister of Canada
articleHtml:
Note: All times local

Ottawa, Ontario

Private meetings.

10:00 a.m. The Prime Minister will virtually attend the National Caucus meeting.

2:00 p.m. The Prime Minister will attend Question Period.

Media appearance

8:35 a.m. An interview with the Prime Minister will air on Toronto’s NewsTalk 1010.
